              <characteristics>
                <characteristic name="Details" typeId="fa11-60d9-4bb8-7538">Discard this card after you win in an assault in which you Destroyed an enemy Tank Team. Remove one adjacent Infantry Team and add the enemy Tank to your force as a Captured Tank unit.

Use  the captured Tank&apos;s normal stats apart from its Is Hit On which becomes 2+. The captured Tank must add +1 to the score needed To Hit when it shoots. A Captured Tank Unit may not Launch an Assault and must always Break Off when assaulted.</characteristic>
