              <characteristics>
                <characteristic name="Details" typeId="fa11-60d9-4bb8-7538">Infantry Teams in Formation cross Minefields safely on a roll of 2+.
Infantry and Gun Teams in this Formations Dig In on a roll of 2+.</characteristic>
